stages.body:
Hi {client_name},

Just a friendly reminder that invoice #{invoice_number} for {amount} is due on {due_date}.

If you have any questions about the invoice or need any clarification, please don't hesitate to reach out.

{payment_instructions}

Thanks for your business!

{contact_name}
{business_name}

Hi {client_name},

This is a reminder that payment for invoice #{invoice_number} ({amount}) is due today ({due_date}).

If you've already sent payment, thank you! Please disregard this message.

{payment_instructions}

Please let me know if you have any questions.

Best regards,
{contact_name}
{business_name}

Hi {client_name},

I wanted to follow up on invoice #{invoice_number} for {amount}, which was due on {due_date} and is now {days_overdue} days past due.

If you've already sent payment, please disregard this message and accept my thanks. Otherwise, I'd appreciate if you could let me know when I can expect payment, or if there are any issues preventing payment that I should be aware of.

{payment_instructions}

Thank you for your attention to this matter.

Best regards,
{contact_name}
{business_name}
{phone}

Dear {client_name},

Your account is now 30 days past due. Invoice #{invoice_number} for {amount} was due on {due_date}.

Immediate payment is required. If payment is not received within 7 days, we may need to suspend services and assess late fees per our payment terms.

{payment_instructions}

If there is a reason for the delay that I'm not aware of, please contact me immediately at {phone} or {email}.

Regards,
{contact_name}
{business_name}

Dear {client_name},

FINAL NOTICE

Invoice #{invoice_number} for {amount} is now {days_overdue} days overdue (due date: {due_date}).

If we do not receive payment within 7 days, we will be forced to escalate this matter to a collections agency, which will negatively impact your credit rating and may result in additional fees.

{payment_instructions}

Please contact me immediately at {phone} or {email} if you need to arrange a payment plan or discuss this matter.

This is your final notice before escalation.

{contact_name}
{business_name}
{phone}
{email}
